We have a pleasure to present you the system produced as a result of the project "Centre for Archivisation and Digitisation of Image and Sound" CADIS. The system allows you to search and order photographs and phonographic collections of the Institute of Art. Currently, the database covers only selected parts of all collections at our disposal and will be successively developed.
